                      ></path>
                    </svg>
                    89K व्यूज
                  </span>
                  <span class="flex items-center">
                    <svg
                      class="w-4 h-4 mr-1"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
